trans-unit.source: Holds information relating to the change of execution status event for an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" />.
trans-unit.target: 保留與 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> 的執行狀態事件變更相關的資訊。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> that raised the event.

Gets the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionResult" /> of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> that raised the event corresponding to the value when the event occurred.
